data.title: Lionel Messi Biography.
data.meta_description: Lionel Messi Biography. - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Lionel Messi is an Argentine soccer player who currently plays for FC Barcelona in Spain and the Argentina national team. He was born in 1987 in Rosario, Argentina and joined the youth academy of Barcelona at age 13 after being diagnosed with a growth hormone deficiency. Since making his professional debut for Barcelona at age 16 in 2004, Messi has established himself as one of the greatest players of all time, winning numerous individual and team honors. He holds the record for most goals scored in a calendar year and has won FIFA World Player of the Year three times. Messi continues to shine for Barcelona and Argentina as one of the world's top players.
